        <mxCell id="cases-items" value="CASE QUEUE:&#xa;• Quick Filters (All, Open, My Open,&#xa;  Auto-Rejected, Pending)&#xa;• Search by: case ID, UCM ID, order ID,&#xa;  customer name/email/phone, account #&#xa;• Filter by: status, priority, type,&#xa;  investigator, date range&#xa;• Sort by: created_at, priority, status&#xa;• Create Case button + modal&#xa;• Export CSV button&#xa;&#xa;CASE DETAIL (multi-tab):&#xa;─────────────────────────&#xa;Tab 1: 🤖 AI Insights&#xa;  • Triage Agent (risk, priority, confidence)&#xa;  • Verification Agent (match/mismatch)&#xa;  • Summarization Agent (brief)&#xa;  • Decision Agent (recommendation)&#xa;  • Confidence Gate indicator&#xa;  • Investigation Score + Risk Factors&#xa;  • AI Degradation Banner&#xa;&#xa;Tab 2: ✓ Verification&#xa;  • Field-by-field match table&#xa;  • Overall confidence score&#xa;&#xa;Tab 3: ⚖️ Disposition&#xa;  • Disposition dropdown&#xa;  • Comments textarea&#xa;  • Submit / Escalate buttons&#xa;  • Reassign (supervisor)&#xa;  • Pipeline Status after submit&#xa;&#xa;Tab 4: 💬 Redshift Chat&#xa;  • NLP query scoped to case&#xa;  • Quick query buttons&#xa;  • Generated SQL + results table&#xa;&#xa;Tab 5: 👤 Customer History&#xa;  • Summary metrics&#xa;  • All cases for customer&#xa;&#xa;Tab 6: 💭 Comments&#xa;  • Comments list + add new&#xa;&#xa;Tab 7: 📜 History&#xa;  • Status change timeline&#xa;  • Audit trail (per-case)&#xa;  • Export JSON/CSV&#xa;&#xa;Tab 8: 🔗 Linked&#xa;  • Linked cases list&#xa;  • Create new link&#xa;&#xa;Tab 9: 🔧 Tools&#xa;  • 12 External tool links" style="text;html=1;align=left;verticalAlign=top;resizable=0;points=[];fontSize=8;fontColor=#424242;" vertex="1" parent="1">
